"For 3D math, Godot provides a :ref:`Plane <class_Plane>` built-in type that "
"handles this."
msgstr ""
"对于3维的情况,Godot提供了一个 :ref:`Plane <class_Plane>` 内置类型来处理这个问"
"题."

